headline: United Airlines, CoreWeave seeks debt deal, Panasonic layoffs
summary: Yahoo Finance host Brad Smith tracks today's top moving stocks and biggest market stories in this Market Minute, including United Airlines (UAL) stock slipping following an outage at Newark Liberty International Airport, CoreWeave's (CRWV) reported pursuit of a $1.5 billion debt deal, and Panasonic's (6752.T) plans to lay off 10,000 workers. Stay up to date on the latest market action, minute-by-minute, with Yahoo Finance's Market Minute.
